summary: SEO Engine V5 BIONIC +300% - Complete validation. All 30 backend API tests passed (100%). Frontend AdminSEO module fully functional with 7 tabs (Dashboard, Clusters, Pages, JSON-LD, Analytics, Automation, Content Factory). Module accessible via /admin-premium sidebar. Shows 9 base clusters (moose, deer, bear, laurentides, abitibi, rut_season, calling, scouting, equipment) with proper filtering and search volume data.

issues: 404 errors in console for some static resources (favicon, manifest) - non-blocking

critical_code_review_comments: SEO Router properly implements all endpoints under /api/v1/bionic/seo/* with LEGO V5 isolated architecture
